    SourceStratagemActivationProfile('phase17s:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309005', 'stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309005', 'gw-11e-phase17e-exact-faction-subrules-2026-27:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309005', 'chaos-knights', 'lords-of-dread', '000010309005', 'TITANIC DUEL', 1, 'epic_deed', 'Your Shooting phase or the Fight phase.', 'One Chaos Knights Character unit from your army that has not been selected to shoot or fight this phase.', 'Select one enemy MONSTER or VEHICLE unit. Until the end of the phase, each time a model in your unit makes an attack that targets that enemy unit, re-roll a Hit roll of 1 and re-roll a Wound roll of 1. Each time a model in your unit makes an attack that targets that enemy unit, if that enemy unit is TITANIC, you can re-roll the Hit roll and you can re-roll the Wound roll instead.', 'matched play same stratagem per phase', 'start_phase', ('shooting', 'fight',), 'friendly_unit', 'friendly_unit', ('CHARACTER',), (), (), (), (), '8cd9988c5db3e4318dc3c035b6870e70355bedc820ed2cb02245be39b54541de'),
    SourceStratagemActivationProfile('phase17s:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309006', 'stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309006', 'gw-11e-phase17e-exact-faction-subrules-2026-27:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309006', 'chaos-knights', 'lords-of-dread', '000010309006', 'TROPHY HUNTER', 1, 'epic_deed', 'Fight phase, just before a Chaos Knights Character unit from your army consolidates.', 'That CHAOS KNIGHTS CHARACTER unit.', 'Until the end of the phase, each time your unit Consolidates, models in it can move an additional 3" as long as your unit can end that move within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.', 'matched play same stratagem per phase', 'start_phase', ('fight',), 'friendly_unit', 'friendly_unit', ('CHARACTER',), (), (), (), (), '5a76a81a2ca6c50f765bc3445b35d5fd312eedc2ffa161cbd9679ef43986dde5'),
    SourceStratagemActivationProfile('phase17s:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309007', 'stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309007', 'gw-11e-phase17e-exact-faction-subrules-2026-27:stratagem:chaos-knights:lords-of-dread:000010309007', 'chaos-knights', 'lords-of-dread', '000010309007', 'CRUSHED LIKE VERMIN', 1, 'epic_deed', 'Your Movement phase, just after a Chaos Knights Character unit from your army ends a Normal move.', 'That CHAOS KNIGHTS CHARACTER unit.', 'Select one enemy unit (excluding MONSTERS and VEHICLES) that your unit moved over during that move and roll six D6: for each 4+, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound. If one or more models are destroyed as a result of this Stratagem, that enemy unit must take a Battle-shock test.', 'matched play same stratagem per phase', 'start_phase', ('movement',), 'friendly_unit', 'friendly_unit', ('CHARACTER',), (), (), (), (), 'e44150edaff54b04a22a3ab4a1df5e2abf7ce0d0e4071d65332cc052dfd49de6'),
    SourceStratagemActivationProfile('phase17s:stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517002', 'stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517002', 'gw-11e-phase17e-exact-faction-subrules-2026-27:stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517002', 'chaos-knights', 'traitoris-lance', '000008517002', 'PTERRORSHADES', 1, 'wargear', 'Any phase, just after an enemy unit fails a Battle-shock test.', 'One Chaos Knights unit from your army that is within 12" of that enemy unit.', 'Roll six D6: for each 4+, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound and one model in your unit regains up to 1 lost wound. RESTRICTIONS: You can only use this Stratagem once per battle round.', 'matched play same stratagem per phase', 'start_phase', ('any',), 'friendly_unit', 'friendly_unit', (), (), (), (), (), 'f603a3fb964cf215cd87600ca2b38075c304d0d72ac02cb7b20fb1f4f86c9de4'),
    SourceStratagemActivationProfile('phase17s:stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517003', 'stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517003', 'gw-11e-phase17e-exact-faction-subrules-2026-27:stratagem:chaos-knights:traitoris-lance:000008517003', 'chaos-knights', 'traitoris-lance', '000008517003', 'CONQUERORS WITHOUT MERCY', 1, 'battle_tactic', 'Fight phase.', 'One Chaos Knights model from your army that made a Charge move this turn and has not been selected to fight this phase.', 'Until the end of the phase, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of melee weapons equipped by your model by 1. After your model has finished making its attacks this phase, if it destroyed one or more enemy units this phase, each enemy unit within 6" of your model must take a Battle-shock test.', 'matched play same stratagem per phase', 'start_phase', ('fight',), 'friendly_unit', 'not_selected_to_fight_unit', (), (), (), (), (), '87e02093c15cf5a978b15f6229db676821b5e50685e73ea7f204a3c1cccc0de4'),
